{"type":"app","meta":{"headers":{"x-nextjs-stale-time":"4294967294","x-nextjs-prerender":"1","x-next-cache-tags":"_N_T_/layout,_N_T_/methodology/layout,_N_T_/methodology/page,_N_T_/methodology"}},"html":"<!DOCTYPE html><html lang=\"en\"><head><meta charSet=\"utf-8\"/><meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1\"/><link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"/_next/static/css/b61f8d66af1e116e.css\" data-precedence=\"next\"/><link rel=\"preload\" as=\"script\" fetchPriority=\"low\" href=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-06b7f1618a9e9933.js\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/4bd1b696-57f101b2865fa45d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/684-b3d1222443067d8d.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/main-app-567b663515746acc.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/874-572f3eebb682cd89.js\" async=\"\"></script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/app/methodology/page-11ee9b3ff711509f.js\" async=\"\"></script><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.googleapis.com\"/><link rel=\"preconnect\" href=\"https://fonts.gstatic.com\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" title=\"IsStraitHormuzOpen? — event feed\" href=\"/feed.xml\"/><meta name=\"theme-color\" content=\"#07090F\"/><script type=\"application/ld+json\">{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\"@type\":\"WebApplication\",\"name\":\"IsStraitHormuzOpen?\",\"alternateName\":\"IsHormuzOpen\",\"applicationCategory\":\"NewsApplication\",\"url\":\"https://ishormuzstraitopen.pages.dev\",\"description\":\"Real-time monitoring of the Strait of Hormuz, integrating market data, news intelligence and marine weather.\",\"operatingSystem\":\"All\",\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"Offer\",\"price\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"USD\"},\"publisher\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"IsStraitHormuzOpen?\"}}</script><title>Methodology — IsStraitHormuzOpen?</title><meta name=\"description\" content=\"How IsStraitHormuzOpen? computes the Strait of Hormuz state: sources, formulas, refresh cadence, limitations, and change log.\"/><meta name=\"author\" content=\"IsStraitHormuzOpen?\"/><meta name=\"keywords\" content=\"Strait of Hormuz,Ormuz,maritime intelligence,shipping,Iran,geopolitics,oil tankers,Brent,WTI,naval,OPEC\"/><meta name=\"robots\" content=\"index, follow\"/><link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"https://ishormuzstraitopen.pages.dev\"/><link rel=\"alternate\" type=\"application/rss+xml\" href=\"https://ishormuzstraitopen.pages.dev/feed.xml\"/><meta property=\"og:title\" content=\"IsStraitHormuzOpen? — Strait of Hormuz Real-Time Monitoring\"/><meta property=\"og:description\" content=\"Is the Strait of Hormuz open? Live monitoring of maritime, market and intelligence signals.\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"IsStraitHormuzOpen?\"/><meta property=\"og:locale\" content=\"en_US\"/><meta property=\"og:image\" content=\"https://ishormuzstraitopen.pages.dev/api/og\"/><meta property=\"og:image:width\" content=\"1200\"/><meta property=\"og:image:height\" content=\"630\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary_large_image\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"IsStraitHormuzOpen?\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"Real-time Strait of Hormuz monitoring\"/><meta name=\"twitter:image\" content=\"https://ishormuzstraitopen.pages.dev/api/og\"/><script>document.querySelectorAll('body link[rel=\"icon\"], body link[rel=\"apple-touch-icon\"]').forEach(el => document.head.appendChild(el))</script><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/polyfills-42372ed130431b0a.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"antialiased\"><main class=\"min-h-screen bg-[#07090F] text-[#E6ECF3]\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-10 md:py-14\"><a class=\"text-[11px] font-mono uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-[#06B6D4] hover:underline\" href=\"/\">← Back to dashboard</a><h1 class=\"mt-6 text-3xl md:text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight\">Methodology</h1><p class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed\">IsStraitHormuzOpen? is a public intelligence dashboard monitoring the operational state of the Strait of Hormuz. Every number on the page is computed from a documented source on a documented cadence. This page explains how.</p><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">1. What we measure</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><p>The headline output is the <strong>Strait State</strong>: one of<!-- --> <code>OPEN</code>, <code>DISRUPTED</code>, or <code>CLOSED</code>. It is derived in real time from the most recent 72 hours of news, weighted by severity, plus the day&#x27;s Brent crude move.</p><p>Alongside the state we publish a <strong>Tension Level</strong> <!-- -->(NORMAL / ELEVATED / CRITICAL) and an <strong>analyst confidence</strong> score in [0, 1] that grows with source diversity and event density.</p></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">2. Sources</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><div class=\"overflow-x-auto\"><table class=\"w-full text-sm border border-[#1E2533] rounded-lg overflow-hidden\"><thead class=\"bg-[#0B0F18] text-[#6B7787] text-[11px] uppercase tracking-wider\"><tr><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2\">Source</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2\">Used for</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2\">Refresh</th><th class=\"text-left px-3 py-2\">License / notes</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">Yahoo Finance</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">Brent crude (BZ=F), WTI (CL=F), Henry Hub (NG=F)</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">5 min</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Public unofficial endpoint; replace with EIA/ICE for production.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">GDELT v2 Doc API</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">Global news article discovery</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">5 min</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Free; attribution requested.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">CNN RSS</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">World + Middle East headlines</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">60 s</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Public RSS; headlines + links only.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">BBC RSS</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">World + Middle East headlines</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">60 s</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Public RSS; headlines + links only.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">Al Jazeera RSS</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">Headlines + summaries</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">60 s</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Public RSS.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">Reuters (via Google News mirror)</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">Headlines + links</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">60 s</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">Reuters direct RSS is paid; mirror is fair-use headline aggregation.</td></tr><tr class=\"border-t border-[#1E2533]\"><td class=\"px-3 py-2 font-medium\">Open-Meteo</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2]\">Wind, visibility, wave height at 26.5°N 56.4°E</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#A9B4C2] font-mono\">15 min</td><td class=\"px-3 py-2 text-[#6B7787]\">CC-BY-4.0; no key required.</td></tr></tbody></table></div></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">3. How status is computed</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><p>The function lives in <code>app/lib/api.ts</code> as<!-- --> <code>deriveStatus()</code>. Pseudocode:</p><pre class=\"mt-3 p-4 bg-[#0B0F18] border border-[#1E2533] rounded-lg text-[12px] overflow-x-auto leading-relaxed\">recent  = events in past 72h\nlast24  = events in past 24h\n\n# State\nif recent matches /closed|closure|blocked|suspended|halted/  -&gt; CLOSED\nelif recent matches /diverted|rerouted|delayed|evacuated/    -&gt; DISRUPTED\nelse                                                          -&gt; OPEN\n\n# Tension\nweight = { low: 1, medium: 2, high: 4, critical: 7 }\nscore  = sum(weight[e.severity] for e in last24)\nif |brent_change_pct| &gt;= 3:  score += 4\nif score &gt;= 14 or state != OPEN: tensionLevel = CRITICAL\nelif score &gt;= 5:                  tensionLevel = ELEVATED\nelse:                              tensionLevel = NORMAL\n\n# Confidence\nsources    = unique(e.source for e in last24)\nconfidence = min(0.99, 0.55 + 0.06 * |sources| + 0.02 * min(|last24|, 6))</pre></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">4. Refresh cadence</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-[#A9B4C2]\"><li>Timeline / RSS aggregator — <strong>every 60 seconds</strong></li><li>News (GDELT) — every 5 minutes</li><li>Brent / WTI / Henry Hub — every 5 minutes</li><li>Weather (Open-Meteo) — every 15 minutes</li><li>Feed health — every 30 seconds</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">5. Public API</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><p>A read-only JSON API is available for embeds and partner sites. CORS is allow-all and responses are cached at the edge.</p><pre class=\"mt-3 p-4 bg-[#0B0F18] border border-[#1E2533] rounded-lg text-[12px] overflow-x-auto leading-relaxed\">GET /v1/status              # headline state, tension, confidence\nGET /v1/events?limit=30     # latest aggregated events\nGET /v1/events?since=ISO    # incremental fetch\nGET /v1/metrics             # markets, weather, event counts\nGET /feed.xml               # RSS 2.0 for journalists</pre><p class=\"mt-3 text-[#6B7787] text-sm\">License: CC-BY-4.0. Attribution required as “IsStraitHormuzOpen?” with a link back.</p></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">6. Known limitations</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><ul class=\"list-disc list-inside space-y-1 text-[#A9B4C2]\"><li>Real-time AIS (vessel positions) requires a paid feed; the map currently uses a simulated shipping-lane animation and is explicitly labelled as such.</li><li>Sentiment is a keyword-matching heuristic. It can mislabel ironic or quoted headlines. Treat as a directional signal, not an editorial judgement.</li><li>RSS deduplication is URL-based; near-duplicate stories from different outlets may still appear separately.</li><li>Yahoo Finance is an unofficial endpoint and may rate-limit during very high traffic. EIA / ICE replacement is on the V2 roadmap.</li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">7. Change log</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><ul class=\"space-y-2\"><li class=\"border-l-2 border-[#06B6D4]/50 pl-3\"><div class=\"text-[11px] text-[#06B6D4] font-mono\">v<!-- -->0.2.0<!-- --> · <!-- -->2026-05-12</div><div class=\"text-[#A9B4C2] text-sm\">Live data architecture: API routes, RSS aggregator, status derivation, public /v1 API, RSS feed, methodology page.</div></li><li class=\"border-l-2 border-[#06B6D4]/50 pl-3\"><div class=\"text-[11px] text-[#06B6D4] font-mono\">v<!-- -->0.1.0<!-- --> · <!-- -->2026-05-11</div><div class=\"text-[#A9B4C2] text-sm\">Initial Next.js port of the static dashboard; visual + i18n only.</div></li></ul></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">8. Disclaimer</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><p class=\"text-[#A9B4C2]\">This site provides information for situational awareness only. It is <strong>not</strong> navigational, financial, military or operational advice. Always verify with official authorities (IMO, NAVCENT, UKMTO, port authorities, your insurer&#x27;s war-risk cell) before making decisions. Predictions are probabilistic and do not represent a forecast of imminent events.</p></div></section><section class=\"mt-10\"><h2 class=\"text-lg font-semibold tracking-tight text-[#E6ECF3]\">9. Contact</h2><div class=\"mt-3 text-[#A9B4C2] leading-relaxed space-y-3 text-sm\"><p class=\"text-[#A9B4C2]\">Corrections, source suggestions, takedowns, press enquiries:<!-- --> <a class=\"text-[#06B6D4] hover:underline\" href=\"mailto:contact@ishormuzopen.example\">contact@ishormuzopen.example</a></p></div></section><footer class=\"mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-[#1E2533] text-[11px] text-[#6B7787] font-mono\">© <!-- -->2026<!-- --> IsStraitHormuzOpen? ·<!-- --> <a class=\"hover:text-[#06B6D4]\" href=\"/\">Dashboard</a> ·<!-- --> <a href=\"/feed.xml\" class=\"hover:text-[#06B6D4]\">RSS</a> ·<!-- --> <a href=\"/v1/status\" class=\"hover:text-[#06B6D4]\">API</a></footer></div></main><!--$--><!--/$--><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/webpack-06b7f1618a9e9933.js\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[87555,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n3:I[31295,[],\\\"\\\"]\\n4:I[6874,[\\\"874\\\",\\\"static/chunks/874-572f3eebb682cd89.js\\\",\\\"910\\\",\\\"static/chunks/app/methodology/page-11ee9b3ff711509f.js\\\"],\\\"\\\"]\\n5:I[59665,[],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n7:I[59665,[],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\na:I[74911,[],\\\"AsyncMetadataOutlet\\\"]\\nc:I[59665,[],\\\"Vie